trans-unit.source: Represents the contents of a WS-Trust BinaryExchange element.
trans-unit.target: 代表 Ws-trust BinaryExchange 之項目的內容。

trans-unit.source: For more information about the element that this class represents, see the version of the WS-Trust specification that applies to your scenario.
trans-unit.target: 如需此類別代表的項目詳細資訊，請參閱適用於您案例的 Ws-trust 規格的版本。

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.BinaryExchange"></xref> class with the specified data and ValueType URI.

trans-unit.target: 下表顯示的新執行個體的初始屬性值。

trans-unit.source: |Property|Value| |--------------|-----------| |<xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.BinaryExchange.BinaryData%2A>|The specified binary data.| |<xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.BinaryExchange.EncodingType%2A>|The specified encoding type <xref:System.Uri>.| |<xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.BinaryExchange.ValueType%2A>|The specified value type <xref:System.Uri>.|

trans-unit.source: The binary data exchanged.
A <xref:System.Uri> that represents the value type of the binary data.
A <xref:System.Uri> that specifies the encoding type to be used for encoding the binary data.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Uri>，指定要用於編碼的二進位資料編碼類型。</xref:System.Uri>

trans-unit.source: binaryData is .
-or- encodingType is .
-or- valueType is .
encodingType is not an absolute URI.
-or- valueType is not an absolute URI.
Gets the binary data associated with the BinaryExchange element.
trans-unit.target: 取得與 BinaryExchange 元素相關聯的二進位資料。

trans-unit.source: This property returns the value of the BinaryExchange element.
trans-unit.target: 這個屬性會傳回 BinaryExchange 元素的值。

trans-unit.source: An array of <xref:System.Byte> that contains the binary data.
Gets the EncodingType URI.
Specifies the type of encoding used to encode the binary data contained in the element.
trans-unit.target: 指定編碼用來編碼項目中包含的二進位資料的類型。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Uri> that contains the encoding type.
This is the value of the EncodingType attribute of the BinaryExchange element.
trans-unit.target: 這是 BinaryExchange 項目的 EncodingType 屬性的值。

trans-unit.source: Gets the ValueType URI.
Specifies the type of the binary data contained in the element.
trans-unit.target: 指定項目中包含的二進位資料的類型。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Uri> that contains the value type.
This is the value of the ValueType attribute of the BinaryExchange element.
trans-unit.target: 這是 BinaryExchange 元素的 ValueType 屬性的值。
